race.comment: HIGH END CASH (2) finished 3 lengths away in third last start over 350m at this track but in a swift 19.09. Hot time latest and looms as the one to beat. ANGRY MURRAY COD (1) missed the frame last time when fourth (19.50) at this track in a Grade 5 H but not beaten far the start prior. Well placed here and should do much better. DAINTREE DAZZLER (6) ran a respectable 19.16 despite finishing fourth over 350m at this track last start. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. DUBROW (5) was strongly fancied last time on the back of some good recent form but could only manage seventh (16.68) at this track. Something for the Multiples: IDYLLIC JAMES (7)
